#. module: point_of_sale
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/point_of_sale/static/src/app/models/utils/indexed_db.js:0
msgid ""
"The connection to the local database was lost. Reloading the page will "
"restore it and prevent any loss of unsaved orders."
msgstr ""
"ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂາດຫາຍ. ການໂຫຼດໜ້າຄືນໃໝ່ຈະຊ່ວຍກູ້ຄືນມັນ ແລະ ປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ຍັງບໍ່"
"ທັນບັນທຶກສູນຫາຍ."

#. module: point_of_sale
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/point_of_sale/models/pos_config.py:0
